column2: Ruko Smart Robots for Kids, Large Programmable Interactive RC Robot with Voice Control, APP Control, Present for 4 5 6 7 8 9 Years Old Kids Boys and Girls
For warranty information about this product, please click here

{'Text': "APP Control                It can easily connect through the app, you can steer the robot by tilting the phone in the desired direction, the robot makes the corresponding action, easy control but very interesting.                Supports Bluetooth Playback                Connect the robot with cellphone by Bluetooth, the robot can function as a Bluetooth speaker to play songs and stories you choose for your children. There is no limit on the number of songs and stories that the robot can play.                Singing & Dancing                The robot's audio is controllable, allowing you to adjust the volume of the music and cute, cartoonish voice. The voice, music, and lifelike dance moves will help children to have more fun.        Read more        LED Emoji                A LED display with a lot of expressions, such as happy, sad, disappointed, etc. These human-like expressions could let children feeling him emotion, It can be a real companion for children.                Recording                While pressing the recording button on the robot and speaking to it, the awesome robot will imitate what you just said.                 Touch Sensitive                When you touch the robot's head, the robot  responds by saying something funny in a lively ,cute voice.        Read more        ABS Material                Made of high-quality ABS material, it is safe, clean and sanitary, and will not have any impact on the health of children.                Rechargeable Battery                The robot equipped with a 3.7V 600mAh rechargeable battery, charge 2 hours for 2-3 hours playing time. It has passed thousands of charging and discharging tests.                Speed \u200b\u200bAdjustable                2 speed adjustments and 2 moving modes of walking forward (sliding & walking) make the movement of the robot more fun and interesting.
